{
  "stem": "7624.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, for me to leave Germany, it was a pleasure, because I always wanted to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As far as I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even as a kid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was reading some books, German books, about the United States, and I was always fascinated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, like I said before, some of the family wanted to get out, and they went out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some went to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some went to the United States.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my father said, it will pass.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It will passe, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Another thing, a little example I will gave you-- that we had a lawyer, a Jewish lawyer, [INAUDIBLE], and he was decorated in the First World War.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a-- Jews were not allowed to be more than a lieutenant in the German army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even the First World War.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was wounded and was decorated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He has an iron cross.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when the Gestapo came, he said, you cannot do that to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm a Germany Iron Cross.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was no excuse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They all went the same way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, we finally left Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We packed everything, and we took the train from-- we went Breslau to Berlin-- Berlin, Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not at all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The German government gave a permission to, to take that ship, St.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Louis, which was a luxury liner, from the American [INAUDIBLE]-- I think it's a German line-- went New York, Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a very luxurious ship at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they gave us that ship to go to Cuba, with the refugees.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Except-- which we never believed or thought of it-- we had to pay round-trip ticket.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We never thought this-- things like this happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You mean, in order to buy a ticket, you had to buy a round-trip ticket.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A round-trip ticket.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
